Package main

Class PartTimeEmployeeBuilder

java.lang.Object
main.PartTimeEmployeeBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
EmployeeBuilder
public class PartTimeEmployeeBuilder extends Object implements EmployeeBuilder

The PartTimeEmployeeBuilder class implements the EmployeeBuilder interface to provide a concrete builder for creating PartTimeEmployee objects.

This class follows the Builder design pattern, allowing the construction of PartTimeEmployee instances through a fluent API. Each method sets a specific property of the employee and returns the builder instance for method chaining.

Since:
1.0
